description: In the shattering conclusion to this epic story, Adam Jensen faces off against his super-augmented former boss, Durant, in a war for the ages...but as with any conflict, casualties will be high and blood will be shed. Will Adam walk out of this alive?
name: Daemonicus Ex

description:
Jedi Masters Qui-Gon Jinn and Tahl, along with Padawans Xanatos and Orykan, were sent by the Jedi Council to Telos IV to quell the threat of civil war - a mission complicated by the fact that Lord Crion, the planet's leader, is Xanatos's father.

Qui-Gon sensed that a Jedi might be involved in the intrigue, and Tahl was attacked by insurgents - one of whom was an Antarian Ranger, supposedly one of the Jedi's closest allies. All the while, Xanatos struggled - torn between his loyalty to the Jedi Order and his desire for acceptance from Crion.

The situation comes to a head when insurgents attack the palace...
name: Part 3

volume.name: Star Wars: Jedi - The Dark Side

description: It's reckoning time! As the sinister plans of ruthless Hayes Bellamy are put into motion, the fate of Coalville rests in Max Damage's overburdened hands. With Bellemy holding the secret to Max's weakness, and with annihilation of the city imminent, can Max finally prove himself to a world that still sees Enemy No. 1? Especially while trying to protect those he cares about most, and...a new sidekick? It's the arc-ending issue that'll change the INCORRUPTIBLE landscape forever! Miss this and miss out!

The face of the enemy is revealed in this high octane, plot twisting issue! The Intrepids come up against their most challenging adversary yet; a many armed mechanized monster from the mind of Dr. Koi!
name: Carbon Calamari

description: Separated into three worlds, the Doctor battles dinosaurs on a flying carpet, Rory pulls the sword in the stone to fight Wild West gunfighters, and Amy joins the French Resistance to fight the Sontarans. Only the TARDIS can join the worlds together, but where is it?
name: When Worlds Collide Part Two
